    <keyword>i18nHelpers</keyword>
    <short_description
  >Internationalization (i18n) utility functions</short_description>
    <syntax>
        <syntax_item>i18nHelpers('convert', potFile, jsonFile)</syntax_item>
        <syntax_item>i18nHelpers('merge', jsonFile1, jsonFile2)</syntax_item>
        <syntax_item>i18nHelpers('sort', jsonFileA, jsonFileB)</syntax_item>
    </syntax>
    <param_input>
        <param_input_item>
            <param_name>potFile</param_name>
            <param_description
      >String: Path to the source .po/.pot translation template file</param_description>
        </param_input_item>
        <param_input_item>
            <param_name>jsonFile</param_name>
            <param_description
      >String: Path to JSON translation file destination</param_description>
        </param_input_item>
        <param_input_item>
            <param_name>jsonFile1</param_name>
            <param_description
      >String: Path to the source JSON translation file</param_description>
        </param_input_item>
        <param_input_item>
            <param_name>jsonFile2</param_name>
            <param_description
      >String: Path to the destination JSON translation file</param_description>
        </param_input_item>
        <param_input_item>
            <param_name>jsonFileA</param_name>
            <param_description
      >String: Path to the source JSON file to sort</param_description>
        </param_input_item>
        <param_input_item>
            <param_name>jsonFileB</param_name>
            <param_description
      >String: Path to the sorted JSON file</param_description>
        </param_input_item>
    </param_input>
    <description>
        <p>
            <b
      >i18nHelpers</b> provides essential utility functions for managing internationalization files. The main functions include:</p>
            <p>- <b
      >'convert'</b>: Converts a .po/.pot translation template file into JSON format for easier manipulation.</p>
            <p>- <b
      >'merge'</b>: Merges two JSON translation files. The entries from <code
      >jsonFile1</code> are added to <code
      >jsonFile2</code>, and entries exclusive to <code
      >jsonFile2</code> are removed.</p>
            <p>- <b
      >'sort'</b>: Sorts and organizes entries in a JSON translation file. <code
      >jsonFileA</code> and <code
      >jsonFileB</code> may refer to the same file if in-place sorting is desired.</p>
            <p
    >This utility is intended for internal use and may be updated over time.</p>
        </description>
